Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:07.98,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,KUDOU SHINICHI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:07.98,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,THE CASE OF THE MYSTERIOUS\NWALL AND THE BLACK LAB
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, want to see my special overhead shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a little advanced for you guys, so don't try this at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was wondering if you\Nsaw me at this park three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At around 10:30 in the morning, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well now, at that time on a weekday, a middle\Nschooler wouldn't have been in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in class, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, were you guys here on Thursday, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seventeen people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number of people you talked to in the last hour after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, I might be able to advise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not an ordinary student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm still an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My childhood friend and classmate's father is a real private eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though that's not saying much, I might be better than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:03:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For instance, aren't those two men\Nstanding over there police detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say much on the younger man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have a hunch on the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Solid build—definitely has martial arts experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A long coat worn by wind and rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dirty, scuffed shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And intent—clear eyes that haven't left you for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything tells me he's a detective, and\Nan old-fashioned type one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? Maybe I can help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Akimoto Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I work at Touto Sanpou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Touto Sanpou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a big company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've become a suspect in a recent murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The incident was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three days ago, on Thursday, at about 10:30 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandmother, who used to dote on me when I was younger...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was murdered at her home in Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 2,000,000¥ was stolen from her dresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard about that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the police said the suspect was someone she knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was actually me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there any reason the police would suspect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took a personal day on Thursday, intending to visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Wednesday night, I ended up going\Nout with a friend and drinking all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drunk, I stumbled to this park near my\Nhouse and passed out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caught a cold, and canceled my trip to my grandmother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what time did you fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10:00 AM or so, for about an hour, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder was at 10:30, and Kamakura is at least an hour away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that if we can prove you were here\Nthen, it would corroborate your alibi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you did tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But during the interrogation, I mixed up my schedule\Nand answered that I was at my apartment at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just shaken up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had just heard my dear grandmother had been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to think, it was on the very day that I was supposed to visit her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police found in their investigation that I wasn't at my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remembering that I had come to this\Npark, I changed my statement, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You become more suspicious in the eyes of the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the police suspect me, it's difficult\Nto get them to search for witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, this is outside their jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two detectives are from Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so you set out to prove your own innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for witnesses all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:07:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, instead of looking on a Sunday, come back on a weekday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, people who walk and jog here during the week will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be ideal to do it on a Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone who might have seen you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about that the whole\Ntime, but I just can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was anyone using the tennis or soccer walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about sounds? Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A black dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I fell asleep, I thought I heard a dog barking, so I looked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I saw a woman pass here with a black dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was she young?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think she was wearing white and a white hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could see it from this brick terrace?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I couldn't see its whole body, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did see its head and rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that it must be at least 50cm tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be a large breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A black labrador...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe a flat-coated retriever...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Possibly even a doberman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's meet here tomorrow morning at 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we're lucky, we'll meet the same woman with her dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you have to go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my "studies" here are more important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'll be skipping class tomorrow morning for an hour or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, don't come crying to me if teacher catches you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the black dog that man saw was Robin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In my neighborhood, there's a woman who always walks a black lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I like dogs, sometimes I'd stand around\Nand talk with her when she's with Robin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She goes every morning from 9:30 for about\Nan hour and walks him in Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is she? Do you know where she lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really know her name or address.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since the back of that wall seems like it's the\Nend of the walking course, I think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, today's looking pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't mean the back of the wall but the front, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The back of the wall is where Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was saying it was the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That road is Robin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wall would block her view and she couldn't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's true. I wonder what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably, that day, for a change...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Akimoto guy must be clairvoyant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how he could see behind the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it. Clairvoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, why would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have your own ideas, but ESP\Nand telepathy are real, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If people really did have those powers, we'd be\Nliving in a world without crime or detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This earth is full of mysteries you can never solve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s ditching class!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Fighting like a married couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it always me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Black lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They should come down this path again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, let's look for witnesses together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you can miss your classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be back by third period.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with lunch, that gives me 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the boy from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let them be for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At around this time last Thursday, did you pass this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, did you see this man, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't believe I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked if we saw this gentleman last Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you all really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm gonna catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, don't be mean to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This should confirm Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that the testimony of three year olds is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:13:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if I can corroborate their story with\Nthe witness that owns a black lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will that be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must have heard us talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I might think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's an "alibi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be about ants (ari).
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.14,Signs,Note,0,0,0,,Note: This is a simple pun on "arigatou" (thanks) and "ari ga tou" (10 ants)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do say, "Thank goodness there are ten ants," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only the teachers had seen me, and not just the kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we did get something to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that's left is the woman with the black lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, she'll come along soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What dreadful crows, right boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is this dog Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is my Robin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you take the path on the other side of this wall last Thursday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At about this time of the day, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this boy is fussy about taking this road every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you take a different path for a change sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please think carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was four days ago, on Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it was this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:16:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember it, last Thursday, it was quite chilly,\Nand Robin saw a crow on the wall just like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Robin is obviously the dog Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the dog was walking on this side of the wall,\Nthere's no way he could have seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Akimoto person must be clairvoyant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see any holes or cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way to see that road...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you should get back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Third period's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have to make this my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't think I can take any more work off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It already looks bad to my manager that\NI had to get questioned by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go at it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do have my pride as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been four days since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've asked everyone that's come by Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no one seems to have seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman's dead sure she was on the other side of that wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I checked out leads in case a different dog might\Nhave been walking in the park at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't find anything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this is any help, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw the black dog, I remember\Nthinking it was a seeing-eye dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A seeing-eye dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen people with black lab seeing-eye dogs there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think they might have been trainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll check that lead out starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's when I remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:20:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I find it's easy to calm down and think in here somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you discover the secret of the Case of\Nthe Mysterious Wall and the Black Lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I spent all of today checking out guide animal centers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't have much to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about some fatherly advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you go to Beika Park, you'll see all kinds of people, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't give me any hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to solve this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they grow up so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} think it was a guide\Nanimal when he saw the black dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that there are a lot of black lab seeing-eye dogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is that the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe playing the violin will pull you over this sticking point?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My young Holmes{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I'm in the mood for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, Holmes didn't play the violin when he was\Nat an impasse, but to pass the time between cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know at least that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hear you play again, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spent all yesterday and finally found it:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The black dog that Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it a guide dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you lie down in the grass like you did that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you as well, detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A guitar case?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:22:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The black dog's true identity is a guitar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In your groggy stupor, the guitar case\Nlooked like a black lab out for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One that had a harness, like a guide dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I was looking at a dog, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I wasn't drunk or sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because I put the suggestion in your mind\Nthat you'd be seeing a black lab beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the same way that Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had\Nseen black seeing-eye dogs here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It made your mind predisposed to confusing the two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, the silhouette does resemble the same shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tested it out yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see the top of her guitar case...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the rocking motion looks like a dog walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you once more:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last week, on Thursday, at 10:30, did you pass down this road?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Usually I don't cut through the park, but I just happened to that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I saw that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe we've established Akimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.11,0:24:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Genjiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.37,0:24:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.33,0:24:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood. On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.08,0:24:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call from HQ: They got the perp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.29,0:24:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it was the work of a home robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.51,0:24:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.26,0:24:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.47,0:24:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.97,0:25:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.27,0:25:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you won't be needing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.28,0:25:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.86,0:25:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be very relieved that the killer was caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.03,0:25:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe you a debt of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.04,0:25:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.46,0:25:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.46,0:25:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.09,0:25:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.67,0:25:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.55,0:25:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this time, my father figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.26,0:25:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe playing the violin will pull you over this sticking point?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.85,0:25:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My young Holmes{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.56,0:25:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.48,0:25:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.07,0:25:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he was a famous detective, too, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.20,0:26:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.70,0:26:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.67,0:26:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Barely made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.92,0:26:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.42,0:26:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.77,0:26:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? It wasn't clairvoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.61,0:26:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.38,0:26:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.63,0:27:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.39,0:27:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.97,0:27:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.06,0:27:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.44,0:27:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was a guitar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.78,0:27:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, Ran and I ended our week-long\Nfight in the spring of 8th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.61,0:27:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea the song would figure\Ninto a huge case three years later...
